embed.title: Please select/react to the BMCC status that suits you.
embed.description:
:notebook: - Student
:mortar_board: - Alumni
Note: Picking a role indicates that you have read, and agreed to our rules, and thus, grants you access to the channels of this server. Happy coding!

embed.title: Select/react to the gender identity which best suits you
embed.description:
This makes it easier for us to make certain channels accessible to you, like AcmW which is a group for Women & non-binaries.
We will work to ensure this club is a safe space for all members.
:blue_circle: He/Him
:purple_circle: She/Her
:green_circle: They/Them

embed.title: React/un-react to opt in or out of the website-programming team!
embed.description:
Howdy fellers! The time has come to develop a new website for the BMCC programming club. By reacting to this message, you'll gain a @role which will be used for communicating on this topic. Programmers of all current skill levels are highly encouraged to join; there will be opportunities for everyone to collaborate in some way.
Happy programming!

embed.description:
Adding a react will add the role.
Removing your react will remove the role.
